Sentencas: An impedance separation analysis of the anode and cathode of a practical solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) is conducted.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Spectroscopy Analysis of an Anode-Supported Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Electro-chemical impedance spectroscopy with a two-electrode setup is applied to an anode-supported intermediate temperature microtubular SOFC composed of a Ni/(ZrO2)(0.9)(Y2O3)(0.1) cermet anode, a La0.8Sr0.2Ga0.8Mg0.2O2.8 electrolyte, and a (La0.6Sr0.4) (Co0.2Fe0.8) O-3 cathode.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Spectroscopy Analysis of an Anode-Supported Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: Measurements are carried out for the cell operated at 700 degrees C with varying flow rates and compositions of the H-2/N-2 mixture gas fed into the anode and the O-2/N-2 mixture gas fed into the cathode.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Spectroscopy Analysis of an Anode-Supported Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: The anode and cathode impedances are thereby separately assigned to low and high frequency impedance spectra, respectively.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Spectroscopy Analysis of an Anode-Supported Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: An equivalent circuit model is applied to the spectra to acquire the polarization resistances and associated capacitances for the charge and mass transfer processes at the anode and cathode and the cell ohmic resistance.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Spectroscopy Analysis of an Anode-Supported Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: The variation in these circuit parameters are then obtained in accordance with current densities and anode gas-feed conditions.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Spectroscopy Analysis of an Anode-Supported Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: In addition, the hydrogen diffusion length correlated with the Nernst loss in the axial direction of the anode substrate tube is estimated.
Titulo: Electrochemical Impedance Spectroscopy Analysis of an Anode-Supported Microtubular Solid Oxide Fuel Cell

Sentencas: These parameters obtained separately and simultaneously for each part of the cell are informative for a detailed analysis and diagnosis of practical SOFCs under operation.
